    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      I'm an English Teacher passionate about crafting engaging lessons. 
      With 3 years of experience and a degree from Higher School of Economics, I infuse vitality into my teaching methods, transforming traditional concepts into captivating learning experiences.
    </Fragment>
