    <Fragment slot="content">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight dark:text-white sm:text-3xl mb-2">About me</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to my educational journey. My work is a testament to my commitment to fostering learning, where each lesson becomes a stepping stone in the path of knowledge.

      </p>
      <br />
      <p>
        I find inspiration in the world around me, whether through the pages of an enlightening book, the intricate details of language structure, or the vibrant diversity of cultures during my travels.

      </p>
      <br />
      <p>If you're curious to dive deeper into my teaching philosophy and methods, feel free to reach out:</p>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="bg">
